{"tid":666953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"綠帽慘汁 狼死男當街木棍毆女人","createTime":"2018-05-16T10:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T02:01:49.000Z","uid":54226,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"be5208cd9f6b13e7754c34a22a9c783b3342c6c6","tid":666953,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/182439_b93ce77656e40e8a7ed3f14abab5d21e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F182439_b93ce77656e40e8a7ed3f14abab5d21e.png&h=32c7213a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男女之間爭吵時有發生，但廣東佛山一名男子疑似因感情問題，當街與女友對質後，竟拗斷支撐樹木的木棍狠下毒手，向女方的腰部和小腿狂打，下手重得更令木棍斷成兩截。有途人報警，男子才停手。<br />\n<br />\n事件懷疑是男子「戴绿帽」而起，網傳的閉路電視片段所見，男子和短髮女子爭吵，繼而怒氣沖沖，直接從路旁拿走一條支撐樹木的木棍，用腳踩成一半，再走回女子身旁。男子越來越激動，接著舉起木棍在女子身上痛打好幾下，手中的手機也甩手飛出，期間木棍也斷開成兩截。<br />\n<br />\n女子在片中顯得十分冷靜，沒有任何反抗，但男子並不罷休，再度拿木棍大力往女方小腿毆打，女子痛到直接倒在地上，男子也沒將她扶起。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，有目擊者看不過眼打電話報警，後來經警方調查，兩人為同事關係，因感情糾紛起衝突。警方表示會檢視女子傷勢，調查釐清男子應負的責任。有網民表示，聽到當時男子生氣問對方「內褲呢？」，女子回應「在他家」，接著男子就失控打人。"},{"pid":"49d6d1677c609f4d977e7694f90886bb1e815fac","tid":666953,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"Source <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/chi/1216374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1216374%2F&d=YyqeJoGqwpmQPnUJQVY3cCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ec61f936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/chi/1216374/</a>"},{"pid":"143d3813af122be97732245b6213a54f5d4f92df","tid":666953,"uid":2566,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">聽到當時男子生氣問對方「內褲呢？」，女子回應「在他家」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a69de4e03a363e8068fb6d13860e2c9aea79210","tid":666953,"uid":54226,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"打得好 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec5a3f2dd42da8a27c1704857709abb47353442","tid":666953,"uid":54226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"睇到fb啲人話打女人唔啱<br />\n男人戴綠帽係男方問題<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935ad3f7b91ab144a1c2864c04f2e3fb9302d0f5","tid":666953,"uid":85557,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"往死裏打"},{"pid":"bbe3a9d9fd71a12081e7e5687e31f59fcd0c1b6f","tid":666953,"uid":176508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"如果真綠係抵打"},{"pid":"cb7750f242ce7b6b79ccae7a4a87d94f28938f31","tid":666953,"uid":41974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"真男人"},{"pid":"29ebba0d6bd69f444b1f977e2c0d008cb1c8d201","tid":666953,"uid":144776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a69de4e03a363e8068fb6d13860e2c9aea79210","tid":666953,"uid":54226,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"打得好 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:29